Adamawa state Governor, Ahmadu Umaru Fintiri as joined many well meaning Nigerians in wishing President Muhammadu Buhari GCFR, a happy birthday as he clocks 77. “Your steady hand in encouraging the nation to go back to Agriculture  has been a source of stability for our economy. Today, many World  Leaders have taken a cue from your stance on Security in Nigeria and  Africa.” “You have done this while staying true to the priorities of the citizens of our beloved Nation. Nigeria is blessed by your service and and the wisdom you bring to High office.” He said. Fintiri prayed that the Almighty endows the President with the courage to continue to be true to himself and the Nation. “Once again, happy birthday Mr  President.” Added. Hinatufe Henry Solomon is a graduate of Computer Science, specialist in ICT Support Services. Henry is also proficient in use of most online journalism tools and Social media management. He currently serve as Information Technology Officer with Africa's Largest TV Network.